Gamma spectrometer / automated

                                                                    - 2470 WIZARD2                                                            








        Characteristics    



Type: 
gamma


Other characteristics: 
automated




        Description    


The 2470 WIZARD2 is equipped with high resolution MCA technology and features superior counting geometry in addition to sample changer robotics. It represents the most advanced design currently available on the market and is intended for the study of a range of gamma emittors. All further information can be easily obtained by going to the products description page.



